                            <div class="panel panel-default">
                                <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading-faq-5">
                                    <h4 class="panel-title"> <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#faq-accordion" href="#faq-5" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="faq-5"> Why should one undergo Blockchain training? </a> </h4>
                                </div>
                                <div id="faq-5" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading-faq-5">
                                    <div class="panel-body editor-content">
                                        <p>The cryptocurrency technology that drives the digital payment like bitcoin, ethereum, and Hyperledger is based on the underlying concept of blockchain. Blockchain is a decentralized, trustless, distributed ledger technology that is now driving the financial market and is in huge demand world over. As a result there is a growing demand for professionals who can use blockchain based applications for businesses. KnowledgeHut brings you this course so that you can understand all about the cryptocurrency technology and market yourself as a blockchain developer. You will learn the basics as well as several advanced concepts of Blockchain including Hyperledger and Highlevel blockchain overview and several other&nbsp;concepts.</p>
